data.description: NEW ROOF< NEW FLOORING<some NEW appliances< NEW KITCHEN COUNTER TOPS< NEW LIGHTING< NEW SINKS< NEW TOILETS, This 5 bedroom RANCHER, has an open floor plan and a NEW ROOF on over 1/2 acre with RV PARKING. Come Enjoy the inviting Great room with vaulted ceilings, natural light and natural gas fireplace. We have both a formal dining area for family dinners or kitchen area for the quick eat and go, and also a fun kitchen Island breakfast bar. The kitchen has NEW flooring and a NEW solid surface counter tops, a pantry, plenty of cabinets, a NEW refrigerator and NEW microwave and NEW oven/range in 2021. The private primary bedroom suite is tucked away from the main part of the house for privacy with vaulted ceiling and attached 5 pc bathroom. The bath has double vanities and large oval soaking tub, for those quiet moments. The laundry room with NEW flooring has space for front end loaders and for a second refrigerator or freezer. There are 2 other bedrooms on the main level and full guest bathroom. As you retire to the Basement, you will be surprised to see how open it is with a huge Family room. There is projector and speaker pre-wired as well as pre-plumbed for a wet bar and step up seating for optimal TV viewing  (can be removed). This open room is large enough for a pool table and a game area. Do not forget the 2 good sized guest bedrooms. One bedroom is attached to a full bath containing a jetted tub just waiting for bubbles. The exercise room has it's own space which is great! The extra 9x11 space in the furnace area is perfect for storage. There are many NEW upgrades such as: NEW flooring on the main level, lighting and light bulbs, sinks and toilets. The back yard has RV/boat parking and a massive dog run and. The yard is level and open with a huge Shed. The rest of the back yard is a blank canvas for football, fire pit, BBQs, Gazebo, patios, play sets, workshop. You choose. All is close to shopping, parks, schools, fire station, restaurants. Come take a look.
